<p>We’ve improved on the previous model, but this came at the cost of doubling the training time.</p>

<p>In the next notebook, we’ll be using the same architecture but using a few tricks that are applicable to all RNN architectures - packed padded sequences and masking. We’ll also implement code which will allow us to look at what words in the input the RNN is paying attention to when decoding the output.</p>
